value:
We identify work-related hazards through a comprehensive approach that includes:

a) Conducting regular worksite inspections;
b) Engaging in direct interactions with our workers and managers to gather on-ground insights;
c) Evaluating incident and near-miss records for trend analysis;
d) Discussing critical safety observations in safety and committee meetings, followed by implementation of corrective and preventive actions;
e) Periodic reviews of potential risk areas for gap analysis and implementation of necessary corrective measures; and
f) Identifying and mitigating risk areas during the issuance of work permits to ensure safe operations.
